sets.title: Pinnacle of shoulders
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Advanced week 10

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
Our aim is peak strength, shape and performance for your shoulders, with a fiery core finisher to cap off an epic session.

Nail your form with the tutorials and push your muscles to failure in the drop sets.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Get your body ready for a strong workout.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: A classic press with a mini drop set to fire up your muscles.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Feel the power building through your full range of motion.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Supersetting rows and flys to work your shoulders in every direction.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Work every last rep from your delts in this descending drop set.

groups.title: Round 5
groups.summary: While your abs crunch, your shoulders must work to stabilize the plate.
